tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE swim_meet_registration (
    registration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_name VARCHAR(50),
    participant_age INT,
    participant_gender CHAR(1),
    event_name VARCHAR(50),
    event_date DATE,
    registration_date TIMESTAMP
);
CREATE TABLE meet (meet_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, meet_name TEXT NOT NULL, meet_date DATE NOT NULL);
CREATE TABLE event (event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, event_name TEXT NOT NULL, event_distance INT NOT NULL, meet_id UUID REFERENCES meet(meet_id) ON DELETE CASCADE);
CREATE TABLE participant (participant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, participant_name TEXT NOT NULL, participant_age INT NOT NULL, participant_gender TEXT NOT NULL);

CREATE TABLE registration (registration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, meet_id UUID REFERENCES meet(meet_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, participant_id UUID REFERENCES participant(participant_id) ON DELETE CASCADE, registration_date DATE NOT NULL);
